name: Isolated EP
description:
this EP was made in April 2020, right when the pandemic strikes Indonesia, containing 4 songs, made in two days.

this EP is about 4 spectrums of being isolated

one. the fortune of having someone that stays isolated with you.
two. what we did to mother earth
three. about what we should quickly do back then
four. about the real super heroes.

(unfortunately) some of these songs is still relevant to my country, and maybe yours. 

wherever you are, stay safe.
